#                 android_widget.zig (AppWidgetProvider) + android_components.zig
#                 (process-global handler registry, JSON event / kv-directive wire
#                 formats). App-facing gossamer_{service,receiver,widget}_bind
#                 exports reuse the webview IPC callback ABI — apps write pure
#                 Rust/Zig/Idris handlers, never touch JNI.
#             [4] Idris2 ABI: Gossamer.ABI.AndroidComponents — terminal-teardown
